    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know people want to help but it doesn't change the reality. it's just me in this house. it feels like i'm just dragging this heavy, broken version of myself around for no reason. like i'm just occupying space that doesn't belong to me anymore. it just feels like such a burden to keep going when the person i'm supposed to be with is gone.",
